data.description: Welcome to the perfect starter, rental or weekend getaway! With its proximity to the marina and the beach it wont disappoint!This home is small but holds a big punch. Open floor plan,fresh paint and wait until you see the backyard oasis! A fully fenced yard with fruit producing trees apple,pear,cherry, and peach. And don't forget the fire pit to enjoy.The fully wired 200 square foot shed holds a sauna and a gym, with other possibilities to create this into a unique space! Come and see it today.
